Description: An R package containing data and analysis results of MoTrPAC PASS1B 
    skeletal muscle (gastrocnemius and vastus lateralis) taken from rats that 
    were either sedentary (SED) for 8 weeks or were treadmill trained for 1 week 
    (1W), 2W, 4W, or 8W. Rats were approximately 6 months old at the start of 
    the training protocol.
